            "ruleText": "1.\u003cstrong\u003eIntroduction to earnings:\u003c/strong\u003e The amount deposited in the interest treasure must satisfy at least one complete cycle to generate interest. If it is transferred out in advance, no earnings will be calculated in that period. For example: the current settlement period is 1 hours, then the amount transferred by 01/01/2025 00:00:01 will generate interest in the first period in 01/01/2025 01:00:01;\n2.\u003cstrong\u003eSettlement cycle:\u003c/strong\u003e The current interest settlement cycle is 1 hours;\n3.\u003cstrong\u003eAPR:\u003c/strong\u003e The current annual percentage rate is 500%;\n4.\u003cstrong\u003eCalculation formula:\u003c/strong\u003e Interest earnings = deposit amount * annual percentage rate / settlement cycle;\n5.\u003cstrong\u003eExample:\u003c/strong\u003eA deposits 01/01/2025 00:00:01 in 10.000, the annual interest rate is 500%, and the settlement period is 1 hours, then the first interest income is obtained in 01/01/2025 01:00:01. The calculation method is as follows:\u003cstrong\u003eFirst interest =10.000*500%/365 days/24 hours*1 hours = 5,707762\u003c/strong\u003e;\n6.\u003cstrong\u003eTransfer threshold:\u003c/strong\u003e Each transfer amount must be greater than or equal to 20 (i.e. ≥20). There is no upper limit for the transfer amount. The more the transfer, the greater the income;\n7.\u003cstrong\u003eInterest cap: \u003c/strong\u003eThe current interest cap can only settle a maximum of 1 cycles. If exceeded, no more interest will be generated. Remember to claim earnings regularly to avoid missing out on more earnings;\n8.\u003cstrong\u003eClaim time:\u003c/strong\u003e It is currently collected the next day, that is, the interest generated on that day cannot be collected until 0:00 the next day;\n9.\u003cstrong\u003eAudit multiple:\u003c/strong\u003e The current audit multiple is 1 times (betting turnover requirements), that is, the interest received needs to be placed before cash can be withdrawn, bet No specific valid platforms,Only the received interest requires auditing, while the principal amount transferred in or out does not require auditing;\n10.\u003cstrong\u003eEvent Statement:\u003c/strong\u003e This function is limited to the account owner for normal game betting. Account leasing, risk-free betting (including betting, wagering, and low-loss betting), malicious arbitrage, use of plug-ins, robots, exploiting protocols, vulnerabilities, interfaces,Group control or other technical means are prohibited. Once verified, the platform reserves the right to terminate member logins, suspend member website usage, and confiscate bonuses and improper profits without prior notice;\n11.\u003cstrong\u003eExplanation:\u003c/strong\u003e When a member receives the Yibao reward, the platform will assume that the member agrees and abides by the corresponding conditions and other relevant regulations. In order to avoid ambiguity in text understanding, the platform reserves the right to final interpretation of this event.",
